org.trellisldp.audit

Class DefaultAuditService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trellisldp.audit.DefaultAuditService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuditService

    public class DefaultAuditService
extends Object
implements AuditService
    An AuditService that generates Audit-related Quads for various write operations.

    This class makes use of the PROV vocabulary and BlankNode objects in a http://www.trellisldp.org/ns/trellis#PreferAudit named graph.
